{"word":"ἐντολή","slug":"ἐντολή","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b><el>ἐντολή, ῆς, ἡ</el></b> [<el><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:ἐντέλλω\">ἐντέλλω</a></el>] ‘a directive for action’, <b>commandment, order, instruction<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>a.</pp></b> <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ freq.\">freq.</a> of the Mosaic code <b><a href='B:470 5:19'>Mt 5:19</a>; <a href='B:470 22:36'>22:36</a>; <a href='B:480 7:8'>Mk 7:8</a>; <a href='B:490 1:6'>Lk 1:6</a>; <a href='B:520 7:8'>Ro 7:8</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>b.</pp></b> of special assignment: to Jesus by his Father <b><a href='B:500 10:18'>J 10:18</a>;</b> to <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> by Jesus <b><a href='B:500 13:34'>J 13:34</a>; <a href='B:500 14:15'>14:15</a>; <a href='B:530 14:37'>1 Cor 14:37</a>; <a href='B:690 2:3'>1 J 2:3</a>;</b> to <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> by religious authorities <b><a href='B:500 11:57'>J 11:57</a>; <a href='B:630 1:14'>Tit 1:14</a>; <a href='B:680 3:2'>2 Pt 3:2</a>;</b> to <a class=\"G\" href=\"S:✎ pers.\">pers.</a> for a special circumstance <b><a href='B:510 17:15'>Ac 17:15</a>; <a href='B:580 4:10'>Col 4:10</a>.<p class=\"pp3\"/>—<pp>d.</pp></b> other types of directives <b><a href='B:610 6:14'>1 Ti 6:14</a>; <a href='B:680 2:21'>2 Pt 2:21</a>; <a href='B:730 12:17'>Rv 12:17</a>; <a href='B:730 14:12'>14:12</a>.</b> <center id=\"nav_bottom\"> <a id=\"left_arrow\" href=\"S:ἔντιμος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> <a id=\"bottom_home\" href=\"S:#1.Table of Contents\">&emsp;&emsp;</a> <a id=\"right_arrow\" href=\"S:ἐντόπιος\">&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;&ensp;</a> </center> "}]}